entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have met Han Solo on Dathomir, he would like you to perform a job on behalf of the Alliance.
entries.journal_entry_description: Han Solo requests your presence on Dathomir.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: [Han Solo] I have an important proposition for you. Can you meet me on Dathomir as soon as possible?
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Speak with Han Solo to see what is going on.
